'''關節炎'''（{{lang-en|Arthritis}}）一詞，常被用來指任何會影響[[關節|關節]]的疾病<ref name=NIH2014/>，[[症狀|症狀]]常包括[[關節疼痛|關節疼痛]]和[[關節僵硬|僵硬]]<ref name=NIH2014/>，其他可能的症狀包括發紅、發熱、{{le|腫脹|Joint effusion}}、患病{{le|關節活動度|range of motion}}縮小​​<ref name=NIH2014/><ref name=CDC2016/>。某些關節炎，除了關節外，也會影響其他器官<ref name=NIH2014Liv/>。發病可能是漸進式，或是突然急性發作<ref name=CDC2016Bas>{{cite web|title=Arthritis Basics|url=https://www.cdc.gov/arthritis/basics/index.html|website=CDC|access-date=2016-09-14|date=2016-05-09|deadurl=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160917131226/http://www.cdc.gov/arthritis/basics/index.html|archive-date=2016-09-17}}</ref>。

關節炎有超過100多種<ref name=Ath2013>{{cite book|last1=Athanasiou|first1=Kyriacos A.|last2=Darling|first2=Eric M.|last3=Hu|first3=Jerry C.|last4=DuRaine|first4=Grayson D.|last5=Reddi|first5=A. Hari|title=Articular Cartilage|date=2013|publisher=CRC Press|isbn=9781439853252|page=105|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Bn_RBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA105|deadurl=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220150711/https://books.google.com/books?id=Bn_RBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA105|archive-date=2016-12-20|access-date=2018-09-02}}</ref><ref name=CDC2016Bas/>，最常見的是[[骨關節炎|骨關節炎]]（退化性關節病）和[[類風濕性關節炎|類風濕性關節炎]]<ref name=NIH2014Liv/>。骨關節炎常隨年齡增長而發病於[[手指|手指]]、[[膝|膝]]和[[髖|髖]]<ref name=NIH2014Liv/>。類風濕性關節炎是一種以侵犯手部與[[足部|足部]]關節的[[自體免疫性疾病|自體免疫性疾病]]<ref name=NIH2014Liv/>。其他種類則有[[痛風|痛風]]、[[全身性紅斑狼瘡|全身性紅斑狼瘡]]、[[纖維肌痛|纖維肌痛]]和[[敗血性關節炎|敗血性關節炎]]<ref name=CDC2016/><ref name=NIH2014Liv/>，以上即為各種類型的[[風濕|風濕]]<ref name=NIH2014/>。

可能的治療方式包含讓關節休息和交替冰熱敷<ref name=NIH2014Liv/>，減重和運動可能有益<ref name=NIH2014Liv/>。建議用藥則依不同類型的關節炎而異<ref name="Ortho2007" />。包括使用止痛藥，如[[布洛芬|布洛芬]]和[[对乙酰氨基酚|对乙酰氨基酚]]<ref name=Ortho2007/>。在某些情況，進行[[關節置換術|關節置換術]]可能有益<ref name=NIH2014Liv/>。

超過3.8%的人患有骨關節炎，類風濕性關節炎的盛行率約為0.24%<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = March L, Smith EU, Hoy DG, Cross MJ, Sanchez-Riera L, Blyth F, Buchbinder R, Vos T, Woolf AD | title = Burden of disability due to musculoskeletal (MSK) disorders | journal = Best Practice & Research. Clinical Rheumatology | volume = 28 | issue = 3 | pages = 353–66 | date = June 2014 | pmid = 25481420 | doi = 10.1016/j.berh.2014.08.002 }}</ref>。在[[西方社會|西方世界]]，約有1-2%的人在人生某個階段會罹患[[痛風|痛風]]<ref name=Lancet2010>{{cite journal | vauthors = Richette P, Bardin T | title = Gout | journal = Lancet | volume = 375 | issue = 9711 | pages = 318–28 | date = January 2010 | pmid = 19692116 | doi = 10.1016/S0140-6736(09)60883-7 }}</ref>。在[[美國|美國]]，超過兩成的人患有某種關節炎<ref name=CDC2015>{{cite web|title=Arthritis|url=https://www.cdc.gov/chronicdisease/resources/publications/aag/arthritis.htm|website=CDC|access-date=2016-09-14|date=2015-06-22|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160922021640/http://www.cdc.gov/chronicdisease/resources/publications/aag/arthritis.htm|archive-date=2016-09-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Pirotta M | title = Arthritis disease - the use of complementary therapies | journal = Australian Family Physician | volume = 39 | issue = 9 | pages = 638–40 | date = September 2010 | pmid = 20877766 }}</ref>，在[[澳洲|澳洲]]則為15%<ref name=ABS2015>{{cite web|title=National Health Survey|url=http://www.abs.gov.au/AUSSTATS/abs@.nsf/allprimarymainfeatures/F6CE5715FE4AC1B1CA257AA30014C725?opendocument|website=ABS|access-date=2017-01-14|date=2015-12-08|deadurl=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170116162239/http://www.abs.gov.au/AUSSTATS/abs%40.nsf/allprimarymainfeatures/F6CE5715FE4AC1B1CA257AA30014C725?opendocument|archive-date=2017-01-16}}</ref>。綜觀來說，隨著年齡增加，關節炎也愈見普遍<ref name=CDC2016/>。關節炎是影響工作的常見原因，並導致生活品質下降<ref name=Ortho2007/>。關節炎的英文源自拉丁文，由代表關節的字根 {{le|arthr-}} 和代表[[發炎|發炎]]的字尾 {{le|-itis|}} 組成<ref>{{cite book|editor-last=Waite|editor-first=Maurice|title=Paperback Oxford English Dictionary|date=2012|publisher=OUP Oxford|isbn=9780199640942|page=35|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=mYicAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA35|deadurl=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220150636/https://books.google.com/books?id=mYicAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA35|archive-date=2016-12-20|access-date=2019-07-19}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Leonard|first1=Peggy C.|name-list-format=vanc|title=Quick & Easy Medical Terminology - E-Book|date=2015|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|isbn=9780323370646|page=160|url=https://books.google.fr/books?id=_h2KCwAAQBAJ&pg=PA160|access-date=2019-07-19|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115052957/https://books.google.fr/books?id=_h2KCwAAQBAJ&pg=PA160|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 分類 ==
依關節炎發病時影響的關節數量，可以分為只有一個[[關節|關節]]發炎的[[單關節炎|單關節炎]]，同時有五個或五個以上關節同時發作的[[多關節炎|多關節炎]]，而介於其間，影響到2到4 個關節的是[[寡關節炎|寡關節炎]]。

[[關節痛|關節痛]]是某些疾病的原發病症與主要症狀<ref name="NIH2015">{{cite web|title=Osteoarthritis|url=http://www.niams.nih.gov/health_info/Osteoarthritis/default.asp|accessdate=13 May 2015|date=April 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518090102/http://www.niams.nih.gov/health_info/Osteoarthritis/default.asp|archivedate=2015-05-18|website=National Institute of Arthritis and Musculoskeletal and Skin Diseases|deadurl=yes|df=}}</ref><ref name="RA1">{{cite web|title=Handout on Health: Rheumatoid Arthritis|url=http://www.niams.nih.gov/health_info/Rheumatic_Disease/default.asp|accessdate=2 July 2015|date=August 2014|website=National Institute of Arthritis and Musculoskeletal and Skin Diseases|archive-date=2015-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150630212818/http://niams.nih.gov/Health_Info/Rheumatic_Disease/default.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Review08">{{cite journal|title=Gout: an evidence-based review|author=Chen LX, Schumacher HR|url=|date=October 2008|journal=J Clin Rheumatol|issue=5 Suppl|doi=10.1097/RHU.0b013e3181896921|volume=14|pages=S55–62|pmid=18830092}}</ref><ref name="AFP2011">{{cite journal|title=Approach to septic arthritis.|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-family-physician_2011-09-15_84_6/page/653|first1=DL|last2=Katzap|first2=E|date=15 September 2011|journal=American Family Physician|issue=6|volume=84|pages=653–60|pmid=21916390|last3=Horowitz|first3=S|last4=Barilla-LaBarca|first4=ML|last1=Horowitz}}</ref><ref name="AS1">{{cite web|title=Questions and Answers about Ankylosing Spondylitis|url=http://www.niams.nih.gov/health_info/ankylosing_spondylitis/|accessdate=28 September 2016|date=June 2016|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160928175058/http://www.niams.nih.gov/health_info/ankylosing_spondylitis/|archivedate=2016年9月28日|website=NIAMS|deadurl=yes|df=}}</ref>，當一個人患有“關節炎”時，通常意味著他們患有下列其中一種疾病，包括：
{{div col|cols=2}}
* [[骨關節炎|骨關節炎]]
* [[類風濕性關節炎|類風濕性關節炎]]
* [[痛風|痛風]]
* [[敗血性關節炎|敗血性關節炎]]
* [[強直性脊柱炎|僵直性脊椎炎]]
* [[幼年特發性關節炎|幼年特發性關節炎]]
* [[成人史迪爾氏症候群|成人史迪爾氏症候群]]
{{div col end}}
關節痛也可能是其他疾病的症狀，在這種情況下，關節炎被認為是繼發於主要疾病的疾病，包括：
{{div col|cols=2}}
* [[乾癬|乾癬]]（[[乾癬性關節炎|乾癬性關節炎]]）
* [[反應性關節炎|反應性關節炎]]
* [[埃勒斯-當洛二氏症候群|埃勒斯-當洛二氏症候群]]
* [[血色沉著病|血色沉著病]]
* [[肝炎|肝炎]]
* [[萊姆病|萊姆病]]
* [[乾燥症|乾燥症]]
* [[橋本氏甲狀腺炎|橋本氏甲狀腺炎]]
* [[乳糜瀉|乳糜瀉]]<ref name=GuandaliniAssiri2014>{{cite journal|vauthors=Guandalini S, Assiri A|title=Celiac disease: a review|journal=JAMA Pediatr|volume=168|issue=3|pages=:272–8|date=Mar 2014|pmid=24395055|doi=10.1001/jamapediatrics.2013.3858}}</ref>
* {{le|非乳糜泻麸质敏感|Non-celiac gluten sensitivity}}<ref name="FasanoSapone2015">{{cite journal |vauthors=Fasano A, Sapone A, Zevallos V, Schuppan D|title=Nonceliac gluten sensitivity |journal=Gastroenterology |volume=148|issue=6|pages=1195–204|date=May 2015|pmid=25583468 |doi=10.1053/j.gastro.2014.12.049}}</ref><ref name=VoltaCaio2015>{{cite journal |vauthors=Volta U, Caio G, De Giorgio R, Henriksen C, Skodje G, Lundin KE|title=Non-celiac gluten sensitivity: a work-in-progress entity in the spectrum of wheat-related disorders |journal=Best Pract Res Clin Gastroenterol |volume=29|issue=3|pages=477–91|date=Jun 2015|pmid=26060112 |doi=10.1016/j.bpg.2015.04.006}}</ref><ref name="CatassiBai2013">{{cite journal|vauthors=Catassi C, Bai J, Bonaz B, Bouma G, Calabrò A, Carroccio A, Castillejo G, Ciacci C, Cristofori F, Dolinsek J, Francavilla R, Elli L, Green P, Holtmeier W, Koehler P, Koletzko S, Meinhold C, Sanders D, Schumann M, Schuppan D, Ullrich R, Vécsei A, Volta U, Zevallos V, Sapone A, Fasano A|title=Non-celiac gluten sensitivity: the new frontier of gluten related disorders|journal=Nutrients|volume=5|issue=10|year=2013|pages=3839–3853|issn=2072-6643|doi=10.3390/nu5103839|pmid=24077239|type=Review|pmc=3820047}}</ref>
* [[炎症性腸病|炎症性腸病]]（包括[[克隆氏症|克隆氏症]]與[[潰瘍性結腸炎|潰瘍性結腸炎]]）
* [[過敏性紫癜|過敏性紫癜]]
* {{le|免疫球蛋白D過多症候群合併反覆發燒|Hyperimmunoglobulinemia D with recurrent fever}}
* [[結節病|結節病]]
* {{le|膠脂質營養不良|Whipple's disease}}<ref>{{cite web |title=膠脂質營養不良 Whipple's disease |url=http://terms.naer.edu.tw/detail/1086741/ |website=國家教育研究院 |accessdate=2020-04-03 |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115053027/http://terms.naer.edu.tw/detail/1086741/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* {{le|腫瘤壞死因子受體有關的週期性症候群|TNF receptor associated periodic syndrome}}
* [[肉芽腫併多發性血管炎|肉芽腫併多發性血管炎]]（和其它[[血管炎|血管炎]]症候群）
* {{le|家族性地中海熱|Familial Mediterranean fever}}
* [[全身性紅斑狼瘡|全身性紅斑狼瘡]]
{{div col end}}

「未分化關節炎」是指臨床上不符合特定疾病類別的關節炎，這可能是某種已知[[風濕病|風濕病]]的早期階段<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Wollenhaupt J, Zeidler H | title = Undifferentiated arthritis and reactive arthritis | journal = Current Opinion in Rheumatology | volume = 10 | issue = 4 | pages = 306–313 | year = 1998 | pmid = 9725091 | doi = 10.1097/00002281-199807000-00005 }}</ref>。

== 症狀 ==
{| class="wikitable" align="right"
|-
! 關節疾病的關節外特徵<ref>Swash, M, Glynn, M. (eds). 2007. Hutchison's Clinical Methods. Edinburgh. Saunders Elsevier.</ref>
|-
| [[皮膚|皮膚]][[結節|結節]]
|-
| 皮膚[[血管炎|血管炎]]{{le|病灶|lesion}}
|-
| {{le|淋巴結病變|Lymphadenopathy}}
|-
| [[水腫|水腫]]
|-
| [[人眼|眼部]][[炎症|炎症]]
|-
| [[尿道炎|尿道炎]]
|-
| [[腱鞘炎|腱鞘炎]]
|-
| [[滑囊炎|滑囊炎]]
|-
| [[腹瀉|腹瀉]]
|-
| 口生殖器[[潰瘍|潰瘍]]
|}
不同嚴重程度的疼痛是所有類型關節炎的常見症狀。其他症狀包括腫脹、關節僵硬、關節周圍酸痛。狼瘡和類風濕性關節炎等關節炎疾病可影響身體的其他器官，導致多種症狀<ref>[https://www.cdc.gov/chronicdisease/resources/publications/AAG/arthritis.htm Arthritis: The Nation’s Most Common Cause of Disability] {{Wayback|url=https://www.cdc.gov/chronicdisease/resources/publications/AAG/arthritis.htm |date=20100130084326 }} Centers for disease prevention and health promotion. Retrieved on 2010-01-24</ref>。症狀可能包括：
* 無法用手或無法步行
* 關節僵硬，尤其早上或關節使用後
* [[不適|不適]]和疲勞
* [[體重下降|體重下降]]
* [[睡眠|睡眠]]不佳
* [[肌肉痛|肌肉痛]]
* {{le|壓痛|Tenderness (medicine)}}
* 關節活動困難

晚期的關節炎常見明顯的繼發性變化。例如關節炎症狀使人難以走動或運動，可能導致後續效應，比如：
[[File:Gout_Signs_and_Symptoms.jpg|thumb]]
* 肌肉[[虛弱|無力]]
* 失去{{le|靈活度|Flexibility (anatomy)}}
* [[有氧運動|有氧運動]]能力下降
除主要症狀外，這些變化可對[[生活品質|生活品質]]造成巨大影響。

===身心障礙===
在[[美國|美國]]，關節炎是[[身心障礙|身心障礙]]最常見的原因，超過2000萬的關節炎患者在日常功能上受到嚴重限制<ref>[https://www.cdc.gov/chronicdisease/resources/publications/aag/arthritis.htm Arthritis: The Nation's Most Common Cause of Disability] {{Wayback|url=https://www.cdc.gov/chronicdisease/resources/publications/aag/arthritis.htm |date=20100130084326 }} The Center for Disease Control. Retrieved on 2015-01-04</ref>。關節炎病患常必須[[缺席|曠工]]（Absenteeism）和看醫生。關節炎可使身體活動變得非常困難而束手無策。據估計，關節炎病例的總社會成本接近1000億美元，其中近50％來自收入的損失，每年關節炎導致近100萬人次住院以及近4500萬人次就診<ref>{{cite web|title=Direct and Indirect Costs of Musculoskeletal Conditions in 1997: Total and Incremental Estimates Revised Final Report (July, 2003)|url=https://www.amazon.com/clouddrive/share/Q6rPMaaZgYQ8IvC02imgAeDTx2mfp5FSBZqVNCqLMnq?ref_=cd_ph_share_link_copy|accessdate=2016-04-06|archive-date=2021-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210827225245/https://www.amazon.com/clouddrive/share/Q6rPMaaZgYQ8IvC02imgAeDTx2mfp5FSBZqVNCqLMnq?ref_=cd_ph_share_link_copy|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

行動不便加上上述症狀，導致難以維持體能活動，從而增加[[肥胖症|肥胖症]]、[[高膽固醇血症|高膽固醇血症]]、[[心臟病|心臟病]]的風險<ref>{{Cite web|title = Rheumatoid Arthritis and Heart Disease Risk: Atherosclerosis, Heart Attacks, and More|url = http://www.webmd.com/rheumatoid-arthritis/guide/heart-disease-rheumatoid-arthritis|accessdate = 2015-06-09|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150327151244/http://www.webmd.com/rheumatoid-arthritis/guide/heart-disease-rheumatoid-arthritis|archivedate = 2015-03-27|dead-url = no}}</ref>。關節炎病患罹患[[抑鬱症|抑鬱症]]的風險也增加，原因可能是多重因素，包括擔心症狀惡化<ref>{{Cite web|title = Coping With Depression and Rheumatoid Arthritis|url = http://www.webmd.com/rheumatoid-arthritis/features/ra-depression|accessdate = 2015-06-09|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150514223122/http://www.webmd.com/rheumatoid-arthritis/features/ra-depression|archivedate = 2015-05-14|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

==診斷==
診斷仰賴醫療專業人員的臨床身體檢查，並可能安排其他檢查如放射檢查和血液檢查，具體取決於懷疑哪種關節炎而定<ref>{{Cite web|title = How is arthritis diagnosed? {{!}} Arthritis Research UK|url = http://www.arthritisresearchuk.org/arthritis-information/conditions/arthritis/diagnosis.aspx|website = www.arthritisresearchuk.org|accessdate = 2015-06-09|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150402061641/http://www.arthritisresearchuk.org/arthritis-information/conditions/arthritis/diagnosis.aspx|archivedate = 2015-04-02|dead-url = no}}</ref>。所有關節炎都有潛在的疼痛問題。疼痛模式可取決於關節炎種類和部位。[[類風濕性關節炎|類風濕性關節炎]]的症狀通常早晨較嚴重，伴有持續30分鐘以上的僵硬<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.niams.nih.gov/health-topics/rheumatoid-arthritis|title=Rheumatoid Arthritis|last=Nancy Garrick|first=Deputy Director|date=2017-04-20|website=National Institute of Arthritis and Musculoskeletal and Skin Diseases|access-date=2019-05-06|archive-date=2020-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218170625/https://www.niams.nih.gov/health-topics/rheumatoid-arthritis|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但在疾病早期，洗熱水澡可能使症狀消失。另一方面，[[骨關節炎|骨關節炎]]的早晨僵硬相對容易被活動和運動緩解。在老年人和兒童，疼痛可能不是主要表現。老年患者只會減少活動，而嬰兒患者則會減少患肢的使用。

疾病的病史引導診斷判斷。重要的病史包含：發作的速度和時間、受影響的關節型態、症狀的對稱性、早晨的僵硬、壓痛、因不活動而有卡住的感覺、加重和緩解因子、其他全身性的症狀<ref name=CDC1/><ref name=RA1/><ref name=AS1/>。身體檢查可能可以確認診斷或暗示有全身性的疾病。放射線檢查常用於追蹤病情進展或幫助評估嚴重度。

[[血液檢查|血液檢查]]和關節的[[X射線|X射線]]檢查常用來幫助診斷。如果懷疑某種關節炎，則應進行特定的血液檢查，可能包括：[[類風濕因子|類風濕因子]]、[[抗核抗體|抗核抗體]]、{{le|可提取的核抗原|Extractable nuclear antigen}}、特異性抗體。

其他影像学检查包含[[醫學超音波檢查|醫學超音波檢查]]、[[X射線電腦斷層掃描|X射線電腦斷層掃描]]、[[核磁共振成像|核磁共振成像]]檢查等。

=== 骨關節炎 ===
{{Main|骨關節炎}}
即「退化性關節炎」，是最常見的關節炎<ref name=Van2010>{{cite journal | author = VanItallie TB | title = Gout: epitome of painful arthritis | journal = Metab. Clin. Exp. | volume = 59 | issue = Suppl 1 | pages = S32–6 | date = October 2010 | pmid = 20837191 | doi = 10.1016/j.metabol.2010.07.009 }}</ref>。大小關節都可患病，包括手、腕、足部、背部、髖、膝；實質上是由於日常關節磨損引起的疾病，但也可能因為受傷導致。一些關節畸形如[[膝外翻|膝外翻]]、[[髖臼|髖臼]]過度覆蓋、髖臼發育不良，也被認為是膝或髖骨關節炎的誘因。骨關節炎開始於軟骨並最終導致兩個相對的骨頭相互磨損。疾病剛開始是身體活動時會有輕微疼痛，之後會變成持續的疼痛，甚至休息時也痛。疼痛可使人衰弱並妨礙病患進行某些活動。骨關節炎通常會影響承重關節，例如背部、膝、髖。與類風濕性關節炎不同，骨關節炎最常見於老年人，骨關節炎最強的預測因子是年齡的增加，這可能是由於軟骨細胞維持軟骨結構的能力下降所致<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Pereira|first=Duarte|last2=Ramos|first2=Elisabete|last3=Branco|first3=Jaime|date=January 2015|title=Osteoarthritis|journal=Acta Medica Portuguesa|volume=28|issue=1|pages=99–106|issn=1646-0758|pmid=25817486|doi=10.20344/amp.5477}}</ref>。65歲以上女性超過30％會有某種程度的骨關節炎。其他骨關節炎的危險因子包括曾有關節外傷、肥胖、久坐的生活型態<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Zhang Y, Jordan J |title=Epidemiology of Osteoarthritis |journal=Clin Geriatr Med |volume=26 |issue=3 |pages=355–69 |year=2010 |pmid=20699159 |pmc=2920533 |doi=10.1016/j.cger.2010.03.001}}</ref>。

=== 類風濕性關節炎 ===
{{Main|類風濕性關節炎}}
[[File:X-ray_of_right_fourth_PIP_joint_with_bone_erosions_by_rheumatoid_arthritis.jpg|thumb]]造成的[[骨侵蝕|骨侵蝕]]<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Ideguchi H, Ohno S, Hattori H, Senuma A, Ishigatsubo Y | title = Bone erosions in rheumatoid arthritis can be repaired through reduction in disease activity with conventional disease-modifying antirheumatic drugs | journal = Arthritis Research & Therapy | volume = 8 | issue = 3 | pages = R76 | year = 2006 | pmid = 16646983 | pmc = 1526642 | doi = 10.1186/ar1943 }}</ref>]]
類風濕性關節炎是一種免疫系統會攻擊自身[[組織_(生物學)|組織]]的疾病<ref name=CDC1>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cdc.gov/arthritis/basics/rheumatoid-arthritis.html|title=Rheumatoid Arthritis (RA) {{!}} Arthritis {{!}} CDC|date=2019-03-05|website=www.cdc.gov|access-date=2019-05-06|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219180752/https://www.cdc.gov/arthritis/basics/rheumatoid-arthritis.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。攻擊不僅針對關節，也針對許多其他身體部位。大部分的傷害發生在關節內膜和[[軟骨|軟骨]]，最終侵蝕該關節兩個相對的骨骼。通常影響手指、腕、膝、肘等關節，且有對稱性（同時發生於右側與左側），如果不及時治療，可能在幾年內導致嚴重[[畸形|畸形]]。好發於20歲以上的人群。兒童罹病時，可能伴有[[疹|皮疹]]、[[發燒|發燒]]、[[疼痛|疼痛]]、失能、日常活動受限<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cdc.gov/arthritis/basics/faqs.htm|title=Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs) about Arthritis {{!}} CDC|date=2019-02-21|website=www.cdc.gov|access-date=2019-05-06|archive-date=2020-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213105331/https://www.cdc.gov/arthritis/basics/faqs.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。早期診斷和積極治療，與發作後長時間未被診斷相比，前者的生活品量較好<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://familydoctor.org/condition/rheumatoid-arthritis/|title=What Is Rheumatoid Arthritis? Symptoms And Treatment|last=staff|first=familydoctor org editorial|website=familydoctor.org|access-date=2019-05-06|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115053051/https://familydoctor.org/condition/rheumatoid-arthritis/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。相關性最強的風險因子是：女性、類風濕性關節炎的家族病史、接觸[[菸草|菸草]]煙霧<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Deane|first=Kevin D.|last2=Demoruelle|first2=M. Kristen|last3=Kelmenson|first3=Lindsay B.|last4=Kuhn|first4=Kristine A.|last5=Norris|first5=Jill M.|last6=Holers|first6=V. Michael|date=February 2017|title=Genetic and environmental risk factors for rheumatoid arthritis|journal=Best Practice & Research Clinical Rheumatology|volume=31|issue=1|pages=3–18|doi=10.1016/j.berh.2017.08.003|pmc=5726551|pmid=29221595}}</ref>。

骨侵蝕是類風性濕關節炎的主要特徵。骨頭通過[[破骨細胞|破骨細胞]]和[[成骨細胞|成骨細胞]]的作用不斷進行重塑。類風濕性關節炎造成關節骨侵蝕的主要觸發因子之一是{{le|滑膜|Synovial membrane}}發炎，其部分原因是產生了促炎性[[細胞激素|細胞激素]]和核因子κB[[配體|配體]]受體活化劑（RANKL）（Th17細胞和成骨細胞的一種表面蛋白）<ref name="Chabaud_2000">{{cite journal|vauthors=Chabaud M, Garnero P, Dayer JM, Guerne PA, Fossiez F, Miossec P|year=2000|title=Contribution of interleukin 17 to synovium matrix destruction in rheumatoid arthritis|journal=Cytokine|volume=12|issue=7|pages=1092–9|doi=10.1006/cyto.2000.0681|pmid=10880256}}</ref>。成骨細胞可以通過RANK/RANKL機制直接誘發破骨細胞活性<ref name="pmid21464945">{{cite journal |vauthors=Won HY, Lee JA, Park ZS, Song JS, Kim HY, Jang SM, Yoo SE, Rhee Y, Hwang ES, Bae MA | title = Prominent bone loss mediated by RANKL and IL-17 produced by CD4+ T cells in TallyHo/JngJ mice | journal = PLOS ONE | volume = 6 | issue = 3 | pages = e18168 | year = 2011 | pmid = 21464945 | pmc = 3064589 | doi = 10.1371/journal.pone.0018168 | bibcode = 2011PLoSO...618168W }}</ref>。

=== 痛風 ===
{{Main|痛風}}
又稱「代謝性關節炎」。痛風是由於[[尿酸|尿酸]]結晶沉積在關節中而發炎。另有一種較少見的痛風性關節炎，是由焦磷酸鈣的菱形晶體所引起的，稱為[[假性痛風|假性痛風]]。早期的痛風性關節炎常發作於單一關節，但隨著時間可以發作於多關節並造成跛行。痛風的關節常會腫脹並失去功能。未成功治療的痛風會相當疼痛，並能使人衰弱<ref name=Becker>{{cite book|last=Becker|first=Michael A.|title=Arthritis and Allied Conditions: A textbook of Rheumatology edition 15|year=2005|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|pages=2303–2339}}</ref>。標準的痛風藥物為降低尿酸生成（如[[别嘌醇|别嘌醇]]、{{le|非布索坦|Febuxostat}}）或增進腎臟排出尿酸（如{{le|丙磺舒|Probenecid}}），如果仍無法控制血中尿酸濃度和痛風症狀時，即為難治性慢性痛風<ref name=Ali>{{cite journal |vauthors=Ali S, Lally EV | title = Treatment failure gout | journal = Medicine and Health, Rhode Island | volume = 92 | issue = 11 | pages = 369–71 | date = November 2009 | pmid = 19999896}}</ref>。

=== 其他 ===
[[敗血性關節炎|敗血性關節炎]]是另一種嚴重的關節炎。臨床表現為突然寒顫、發燒、關節痛。疾病是由身體其他部位的[[細菌|細菌]]引起的，必須迅速診斷並及時治療，以防止不可逆的關節損害<ref>[http://www.arthritis.org/ Severe Arthritis Disease Facts] {{Wayback|url=http://www.arthritis.org/ |date=20070423120449 }} Retrieved on 2010-02-05</ref>。

[[乾癬|乾癬]]可發展為[[乾癬性關節炎|乾癬性關節炎]]。大多數病患會先出現[[皮膚|皮膚]]問題，然後發展為關節炎。典型特徵是持續的關節痛、僵硬、腫脹。這個疾病會反覆發作與進入緩解期，但無法[[治癒|治癒]]。一小部分人會發展成嚴重疼痛的破壞性關節炎，損壞手部小關節，可導致永久性的手功能喪失<ref>[http://www.mayoclinic.com/health/psoriatic-arthritis/DS00476/DSECTION=symptoms Psoriatic Arthritis] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mayoclinic.com/health/psoriatic-arthritis/DS00476/DSECTION=symptoms |date=20100209073725 }} Mayo Clinic. Retrieved on 2010-02-05</ref>。

== 治療 ==
目前尚無治癒類風濕性關節炎<ref>{{cite web |title=Rheumatoid arthritis (RA): Prognosis |url=https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/323631 |website=Medical News Today |accessdate=2020-04-05 |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115053109/https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/323631 |dead-url=no }}</ref>或骨關節炎<ref>{{cite web |title=Osteoarthritis Treatment and support |url=https://www.nhs.uk/conditions/osteoarthritis/treatment/ |website=NHS UK |accessdate=2020-04-05 |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115053116/https://www.nhs.uk/conditions/osteoarthritis/treatment/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>的方法。治療方法取決於關節炎的類型，可包括[[物理治療|物理治療]]、生活型態的改變（運動和體重控制）、[[護具|護具]]、[[藥物|藥物]]治療。具侵蝕性的關節炎可能需要進行關節置換術。藥物可幫助減輕發炎與疼痛。

=== 物理治療與職能治療 ===
各研究顯示關節運動可以明顯改善長期疼痛。此外，關節運動有助於維持該關節和整個人的健康<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Ettinger WH, Burns R, Messier SP, Applegate W, Rejeski WJ, Morgan T, Shumaker S, Berry MJ, O'Toole M, Monu J, Craven T | title = A randomized trial comparing aerobic exercise and resistance exercise with a health education program in older adults with knee osteoarthritis. The Fitness Arthritis and Seniors Trial (FAST) | journal = JAMA: The Journal of the American Medical Association | volume = 277 | issue = 1 | pages = 25–31 | year = 1997 | pmid = 8980206 | doi = 10.1001/jama.1997.03540250033028 }}</ref>。

病患可以從[[物理治療|物理治療]]和[[職能治療|職能治療]]中受益。物理治療已被證明可以顯著幫助晚期病患改善功能、減輕疼痛、延緩對外科手術的需求<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Fransen M, Crosbie J, Edmonds J | title = Physical therapy is effective for patients with osteoarthritis of the knee: a randomized controlled clinical trial (2001) | journal = J. Rheumatol. | volume = 28 | issue = 1 | pages = 156–64 | date = January 2001 | pmid = 11196518 | url = http://www.jrheum.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=11196518 | access-date = 2019-11-03 | archive-date = 2021-08-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210827225246/https://www.jrheum.org/content/28/1/156.long | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[物理治療師|物理治療師]]引導的運動被證明比藥物能更有效地治療[[膝|膝]]骨關節炎。運動常著重在提高肌肉力量、耐力、靈活度。運動也可用來訓練平衡。職能治療可以協助活動，製作輔具改善患處的使用來減少其失能。輔具有現成的，也可量身訂做<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.aota.org/About-Occupational-Therapy/Professionals/RDP/assistive-technology.aspx|title=The Role of Occupational Therapy in Providing Assistive Technology Devices and Services|last=|first=|date=2018|website=www.aota.org|access-date=2018-04-08|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115053125/https://www.aota.org/About-Occupational-Therapy/Professionals/RDP/assistive-technology.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

需要進行進一步研究確認{{le|經皮電刺激|Transcutaneous electrical nerve stimulation}}對膝骨關節炎的疼痛控制<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Rutjes AW, Nüesch E, Sterchi R, Kalichman L, Hendriks E, Osiri M, Brosseau L, Reichenbach S, Jüni P | title = Transcutaneous electrostimulation for osteoarthritis of the knee | journal = The Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews | issue = 4 | pages = CD002823 | date = October 2009 | pmid = 19821296 | doi = 10.1002/14651858.CD002823.pub2 | url = http://boris.unibe.ch/30337/1/Rutjes%20CochraneLibrary%202009.pdf | access-date = 2019-11-03 | archive-date = 2020-09-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200918005132/https://boris.unibe.ch/30337/1/Rutjes%20CochraneLibrary%202009.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

可考慮使用{{le|低功率雷射|Low-level laser therapy}}來減輕與關節炎有關的疼痛和僵硬<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Brosseau L, Robinson V, Wells G, Debie R, Gam A, Harman K, Morin M, Shea B, Tugwell P | title = Low level laser therapy (Classes I, II and III) for treating rheumatoid arthritis | journal = The Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews | issue = 4 | pages = CD002049 | date = October 2005 | pmid = 16235295 | doi = 10.1002/14651858.CD002049.pub2 }}</ref>。

{{le|脈衝電磁場治療|Pulsed electromagnetic field therapy}}有初步證據支持改善關節功能，但沒有證據顯示會改善骨關節炎的疼痛<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Vavken P, Arrich F, Schuhfried O, Dorotka R | title = Effectiveness of pulsed electromagnetic field therapy in the management of osteoarthritis of the knee: a meta-analysis of randomized controlled trials | journal = Journal of Rehabilitation Medicine | volume = 41 | issue = 6 | pages = 406–11 | date = May 2009 | pmid = 19479151 | doi = 10.2340/16501977-0374 }}</ref>。

=== 藥物 ===
有幾種類型的[[藥物|藥物]]可用於治療關節炎。通常治療從副作用最少的藥物開始，如果療效不足，再調整使用其他藥物<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.arthritistoday.org/treatments/drug-guide/index.php|title=Arthritis Drugs|work=arthritistoday.org|accessdate=2010-07-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100722013235/http://www.arthritistoday.org/treatments/drug-guide/index.php|archivedate=2010-07-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

針對不同類型的關節炎，所用藥物可能不同。例如，骨關節炎的一線治療是[[乙醯胺酚|乙醯胺酚]]，而{{le|發炎性關節炎|Inflammatory arthritis}}（如類風濕性關節炎和[[乾癬性關節炎|乾癬性關節炎]]）可採用[[非類固醇消炎止痛藥|非類固醇消炎止痛藥]]（NSAIDs），如[[布洛芬|布洛芬]]。[[鴉片類藥物|鴉片類藥物]]和非類固醇消炎止痛藥的耐受性可能較差<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Reid MC, Shengelia R, Parker SJ | title = Pharmacologic management of osteoarthritis-related pain in older adults | journal = The American Journal of Nursing | volume = 112 | issue = 3 Suppl 1 | pages = S38–43 | date = Mar 2012 | pmid = 22373746 | pmc = 3733545 | doi=10.1097/01.NAJ.0000412650.02926.e3}}</ref>，但局部劑型（如貼布、[[凝膠|凝膠]]、噴劑）比口服劑型具有更好的安全性。對於更嚴重的骨關節炎病例，可以考慮[[關節注射|關節注射]][[皮質類固醇|皮質類固醇]]<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Taruc-Uy|first=Rafaelani L.|last2=Lynch|first2=Scott A.|date=December 2013|title=Diagnosis and Treatment of Osteoarthritis|journal=Primary Care: Clinics in Office Practice|volume=40|issue=4|pages=821–836|doi=10.1016/j.pop.2013.08.003|pmid=24209720}}</ref>或[[玻尿酸|玻尿酸]]。

治療類風濕性關節炎的藥物可包含[[靜脈注射|靜脈注射]]皮質類固醇和[[單株抗體|單株抗體]]。由於類風濕性關節炎與[[自體免疫|自體免疫]]有關，所以不只止痛藥和消炎藥，還包括另一類稱為{{le|疾病調節抗風濕藥|Disease-modifying antirheumatic drug}}（DMARDs）的藥物。DMARDs旨在通過啟動[[後天免疫系統|後天免疫反應]]來減緩類風濕性關節炎的進程，其中一部分是仰賴[[輔助型T細胞|輔助型T細胞]]，特別是Th17細胞<ref name="pmid23383714">{{cite journal|vauthors=Kurebayashi Y, Nagai S, Ikejiri A, Koyasu S|year=2013|title=Recent advances in understanding the molecular mechanisms of the development and function of Th17 cells|journal=Genes Cells|volume=18|issue=4|pages=247–65|doi=10.1111/gtc.12039|pmc=3657121|pmid=23383714}}</ref>。Th17細胞大量存在於關節內的骨破壞部位並產生發炎性細胞激素，例如[[白血球介素|白血球介素]]17（IL-17）<ref name="Chabaud_2000" />。

=== 外科手術 ===
自1950年代以來，許多[[外科手術|外科手術]]已被納入關節炎的治療，如膝關節或髖關節置換術。膝骨關節炎的[[關節鏡|關節鏡]]手術未能比物理治療和藥物治療帶來額外好處<ref name="pmid18784099">{{cite journal |vauthors=Kirkley A, Birmingham TB, Litchfield RB, Giffin JR, Willits KR, Wong CJ, Feagan BG, Donner A, Griffin SH, D'Ascanio LM, Pope JE, Fowler PJ | title = A randomized trial of arthroscopic surgery for osteoarthritis of the knee | journal = N. Engl. J. Med. | volume = 359 | issue = 11 | pages = 1097–107 | year = 2008 | pmid = 18784099 | doi = 10.1056/NEJMoa0708333 }}</ref>。

=== 輔具 ===
手關節炎的病人可能連簡單的[[日常生活活動|日常活動]]都會遭遇困難，例如轉動鑰匙或打開罐子。有特製的[[輔具|輔具]]可幫助完成這些工作<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.everydayhealth.com/arthritis-pictures/10-terrific-arthritis-gadgets.aspx|title=10 Terrific Arthritis Gadgets - Arthritis Center - Everyday Health|website=EverydayHealth.com|access-date=2019-03-08|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115053240/https://www.everydayhealth.com/arthritis-pictures/10-terrific-arthritis-gadgets.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但它們通常比具有相同功能的常規產品昂貴。現在可以使用3D列印輔具作為[[開源硬體|開源硬體]]以降低患者的花費<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://orthofeed.com/2018/12/15/3-d-printing-offers-helping-hand-to-people-with-arthritis/|title=3-D Printing Offers Helping Hand to People with Arthritis|date=2018-12-15|website=OrthoFeed|access-date=2019-03-08|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115053144/https://orthofeed.com/2018/12/15/3-d-printing-offers-helping-hand-to-people-with-arthritis/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Gallup N, Bow JK, Pearce JM | title = Economic Potential for Distributed Manufacturing of Adaptive Aids for Arthritis Patients in the U.S | journal = Geriatrics | volume = 3 | issue = 4 | pages = 89 | date = December 2018 | pmid = 31011124 | pmc = 6371113 | doi = 10.3390/geriatrics3040089 }}</ref>。輔具可幫助關節炎患者，多數關節炎患者需要並使用它們<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Yeung KT, Lin CH, Teng YL, Chen FF, Lou SZ, Chen CL | title = Use of and Self-Perceived Need for Assistive Devices in Individuals with Disabilities in Taiwan | journal = PLOS ONE | volume = 11 | issue = 3 | pages = e0152707 | date = 2016-03-29 | pmid = 27023276 | pmc = 4811424 | doi = 10.1371/journal.pone.0152707 | bibcode = 2016PLoSO..1152707Y }}</ref>。

== 流行病學 ==
關節炎主要是老年人的疾病，但兒童也可能受到影響<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://medlineplus.gov/ency/article/000451.htm|title=Juvenile idiopathic arthritis: MedlinePlus Medical Encyclopedia|website=medlineplus.gov|access-date=2019-05-06|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219181251/https://medlineplus.gov/ency/article/000451.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。無論在任何的年齡層、[[人種|人種]]、[[族群|族群]]、文化，女性都比男性更常患有關節炎。[[美國疾病管制與預防中心|美國疾病管制與預防中心]]基於2013－2015年數據的一項調查，有5440萬（22.7%）成年人被醫師診斷關節炎，還有2370萬人（佔關節炎病患的43.5%）有關節炎引起的活動受限，隨著[[人口老化|人口老化]]，這些數值可能會再增加。患有心臟病、糖尿病、肥胖症的成年人，關節炎盛行率高於平均水準（分別為49.3%、47.1%、30.6%）<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Barbour|first=Kamil E.|last2=Helmick|first2=Charles G.|last3=Boring|first3=Michael|last4=Brady|first4=Teresa J.|date=2017-03-10|title=Vital Signs: Prevalence of Doctor-Diagnosed Arthritis and Arthritis-Attributable Activity Limitation — United States, 2013–2015|journal=MMWR. Morbidity and Mortality Weekly Report|volume=66|issue=9|pages=246–253|doi=10.15585/mmwr.mm6609e1|issn=0149-2195|pmc=5687192|pmid=28278145}}</ref>。

從1990年到2010年，因肌肉骨骼疾患引起的身體失能增加了45%，其中，骨關節炎是增長最快的主要疾病<ref>{{cite journal | title = GBD 2010 country results: a global public good | journal = Lancet | volume = 381 | issue = 9871 | pages = 965–70 | date = March 2013 | pmid = 23668561 | doi = 10.1016/S0140-6736(13)60283-4 | author1 = GBD 2010 Country Collaboration }}</ref>。許多關於肌肉骨骼疾病盛行率上升的報告缺乏和低估了來自[[非洲|非洲]]的數據。一項系統回顧報告評估了非洲的關節炎盛行率，包括二十項基於人群的研究和七項基於醫院的研究<ref>{{cite journal|title=Prevalence of Arthritis in Africa: A Systematic Review and Meta-Analysis|date=4 August 2015|journal=PLOS ONE|issue=8|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0133858|volume=10|pages=e0133858|bibcode=2015PLoSO..1033858U|pmc=4524637|pmid=26241756|vauthors=Usenbo A, Kramer V, Young T, Musekiwa A}}</ref>。大部分研究（十二項）來自[[南非|南非]]，九項研究有良好品質，十一項研究品質中等，七項研究品質較差，其盛行率如下：

*類風濕性關節炎：[[阿爾及利亞|阿爾及利亞]]城市地區為0.1%；[[剛果民主共和國|剛果民主共和國]]城市地區為0.6%；南非城市和農村地區分別為2.5%和0.07%；[[埃及|埃及]]農村地區為0.3%；[[萊索托|萊索托]]農村地區為0.4%。
*骨關節炎：南非城市地區為55.1%；65歲以上南非人介於29.5%－82.7%之間。
**膝骨關節炎在所有類型的骨關節炎中盛行率最高，在南非農村地區為33.1%。
*僵直性脊椎炎：在南非農村地區為0.1%。
*乾癬性關節炎：在南非城市地區為4.4%。
*痛風：南非城市地區為0.7%。
*幼年特發性關節炎：埃及城市地區為0.3%。

== 歷史 ==
從[[恐龍|恐龍]]的研究中發現有骨關節炎和潛在的發炎性關節炎的證據<ref name="DeLisaGans2005">{{cite book|author1=Joel A. DeLisa|author2=Bruce M. Gans|author3=Nicholas E. Walsh|title=Physical Medicine and Rehabilitation: Principles and Practice|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=1sWk1GYCvKoC&pg=PA765|year=2005|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|isbn=978-0-7817-4130-9|pages=765–|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115053248/https://books.google.com/books?id=1sWk1GYCvKoC&pg=PA765|archivedate=2020-11-15|access-date=2019-11-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Blumberg BS, Sokoloff L |title=Coalescence of caudal vertebrae in the giant dinosaur Diplodocus |journal=Arthritis Rheum. |volume=4 |issue= 6|pages=592–601 |year=1961 |pmid=13870231 |doi=10.1002/art.1780040605}}</ref>。人類的關節炎最早可追溯到[[前5千紀|公元前4500年]]，早期的研究報告中，關節炎常被認為是史前人類最常見的疾病<ref name="Bridges">{{cite journal | author=Bridges PS | title=Prehistoric Arthritis in the Americas | url=https://archive.org/details/sim_annual-review-of-anthropology_1992_21/page/67 | journal=Annual Review of Anthropology | year=1992| volume=21 |pages=67–91 | doi=10.1146/annurev.an.21.100192.000435}}</ref>，在[[田納西州|田納西州]]和現在[[奧拉西_(堪薩斯州)|堪薩斯州奧拉西]]部分地區的[[美洲原住民|美洲原住民]]骨骼遺骸就有這樣的發現。整個歷史上都能發現關節炎的證據，比如從現代[[義大利|義大利]]和[[奧地利|奧地利]]邊界發現的[[木乃伊|木乃伊]][[冰人奧茲|冰人奧茲]]（約公元前3000年）到埃及的木乃伊（約公元前2590年）都有<ref>[http://www.news-medical.net/health/Arthritis-History.aspx Arthritis History] {{Wayback|url=http://www.news-medical.net/health/Arthritis-History.aspx |date=20100130200315 }} Medical News</ref>。

公元1715年，{{le|威廉·穆斯格雷夫|William Musgrave}}發表他最重要的醫學著作《關節炎症狀》（De arthritide symptomatica）第二版，談及關節炎及其影響<ref name=ODNB>Alick Cameron, "Musgrave, William (1655–1721)", Oxford Dictionary of National Biography, Oxford University Press, Sept 2004</ref>。法國婦女庇護所的28歲住院醫師奧古斯丁·雅各布·蘭德雷·博韋（Augustin Jacob Landré-Beauvais）是第一個描述類風濕性關節炎症狀的人，儘管他誤將之歸類為痛風，但他的論文激勵其他人進一步研究該疾病<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Entezami P, Fox DA, Clapham PJ, Chung KC | title = Historical perspective on the etiology of rheumatoid arthritis | journal = Hand Clinics | volume = 27 | issue = 1 | pages = 1–10 | date = February 2011 | pmid = 21176794 | pmc = 3119866 | doi = 10.1016/j.hcl.2010.09.006 }}</ref>。

